**Overview**

This dashboard shows an overview of Identity & Access Management (IAM) events relate to the supervision of the system's authentication and access control model.

Please visit the [Identity & Access Management](https://schema.ocsf.io/1.0.0-rc.3/categories/iam) documentation for more information.

[**Integration Page**](/app/integrations/detail/amazon_security_lake/overview)
